; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the lots.empty() continue path in lot matching.
; AAPL has COMMODITY_SAW_ANNOTATED from an annotated buy in a different
; account, but Assets:Brokerage only holds unannotated AAPL, so no
; matching lots exist and the code continues without splitting.

2024/01/01 Buy annotated in different account
    Assets:Other    10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Buy unannotated in brokerage
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Sell from brokerage
    Assets:Brokerage    -3 AAPL @ $160.00
    Assets:Cash

test --lot-matching fifo reg Assets:Brokerage
24-Jan-15 Buy unannotated in .. Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL       5 AAPL
24-Feb-01 Sell from brokerage   Assets:Brokerage            -3 AAPL       2 AAPL
end test
